<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<%@ include file="/WEB-INF/views/include/head.jsp" %>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>카카오계정으로 가입하기</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://bootswatch.com/5/minty/bootstrap.min.css">
<style type="text/css">

body , html {

width:100%;
height:100%;
}

body {

background-color: rgb(97, 191, 173);


}


.wrap {

width:100%;
height:100%;
display:flex;
justify-content: center;
